description: Let's face it, getting your bike stolen sucks. Using a U-lock to secure it is the first step to a long and happy life with your bike. The Ultra 410 U-lock is hard to cut or pry open, so you'll find your ride just where you left it.12mm diameter hardened steel shackle.Double-bolted lock requires two cuts to remove.Shackle depth is 23cm and width is 17cm.SH 34 carrier fits24-35 mm tubes.2 keys included to ensure you have a backup if one goes missing.Abus security rating of 8/15.
name: Abus Ultra 410 SH34 U-Lock 12mm X 170mm
